switching to vim:
    http://stevelosh.com/blog/2010/09/coming-home-to-vim/

Link .vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc


Add submodules to bundle by:
    git submodule add <REPO> bundle/<BUNDLE NAME>
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

    ex:
        git submodule add https://github.com/altercation/vim-colors-solarized.git bundle/vim-colors-solarize
        git submodule init
        git submodule update
